    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Welcome to beautiful Kazera!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858200/extras/00dca89a85a2223e3e775f53fe532beb.avif?t=1771908517\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858200/extras_big/00dca89a85a2223e3e775f53fe532beb.webp?t=1771908517 width=1560 height=1560 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Vermillion Empire has lead humanity to war with the magical Kazaki for decades.  The Starknight, Razizal, has held off Vermillion's advances for hundreds of years, but the Empire has prepared a masterstroke to turn the tides for good.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858200/extras/d35fbdda47edd1f38c9fb0ceef5bd024.avif?t=1771908517\" width=1282 height=1656 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >KAZAK is an RPG inspired by the 90s, with battles inspired by the Mario &amp; Luigi RPG series.  There are no random encounters, with enemies being visible on the map and you can interact with them to gain an advantage in battle.  There are 3 playable characters, each with unique strengths and weaknesses.  Equip up to 4 skills per character to use in battle.  Each skill has advantages and disadvantages such as raising or lowing stats, and enemies have weaknesses themselves that can be exploited.  There is no MP!  Battle revolves around the mana gauge, inspired by the fighting game genre.  Attack or successfully avoid attacks to build meter and defeat your foes with super moves, while keeping their mana meters down or else you'll be vulnerable to a foe's super move.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858200/extras/1c7a7cd6347d80921b4c6e6efca9ca0b.avif?t=1771908517\" width=200 height=359 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">★★★<strong>HOW TO PLAY</strong>★★★</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858200/extras/844d2cfe26e95260b7389313fb8e240d.avif?t=1771908517\" width=96 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In battle, each character has a unique button assigned to them, called the action button.  This button is essential to survival!  When an enemy goes in for an attack, you can DODGE with the action button!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858200/extras/f9fea5b95608009426764ddfb25375ad.avif?t=1771908517\" width=460 height=407 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">If you aren't smart about your reactions and timing, you'll take a hit and can be afflicted with nasty status effects!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858200/extras/435fc2734f2c52c57cca149ba412f057.avif?t=1771908517\" width=490 height=312 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Some enemy attacks require you to deflect them, which often times does damage to the attacker!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858200/extras/53371b99e82564a88c7261e46d63f643.avif?t=1771908517\" width=451 height=274 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Deflecting will leave you vulnerable for a few seconds afterwards though, so make sure you don't miss!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858200/extras/208e049d7bf27d73e963fb2fdee28bdb.avif?t=1771908517\" width=276 height=472 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">There can be other unorthodox situations where you need to hit the action button, so stay alert!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858200/extras/8b8a709e3c123d2d9300686c70487b54.avif?t=1771908517\" width=333 height=225 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858200/extras/a270ed1090e83326275b6a9a64ba6653.avif?t=1771908517\" width=368 height=262 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">★★★<strong>READY?</strong>★★★</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858200/extras/f73b8bfc19385ec1ab2909f83eb7ff8e.poster.avif?t=1771908517\" width=800 height=612 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858200/extras/f73b8bfc19385ec1ab2909f83eb7ff8e.webm?t=1771908517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858200/extras/f73b8bfc19385ec1ab2909f83eb7ff8e.mp4?t=1771908517\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858200/extras/926726c57d4110bb57ed38e5aa49f158.poster.avif?t=1771908517\" width=800 height=612 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858200/extras/926726c57d4110bb57ed38e5aa49f158.webm?t=1771908517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858200/extras/926726c57d4110bb57ed38e5aa49f158.mp4?t=1771908517\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
